import {FloatingLabel, Form} from 'react-bootstrap'

export const FloatingLabelsSearch = (props) => {

   return <>

        <FloatingLabel
            controlId="floatingInput"
            label="Search"
            className="mb-3"
        >
            
            <Form.Control
                type="search" 
                name="search"
                placeholder="Search" 
                value = {props.val}
                onChange={props.handleChange}
            />
     
        </FloatingLabel>

    </>
}
